<1ST_LINE>r w AM-CollisionAvoidance     10-28 0460</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Collision Avoidance,440</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>New Airline Collision Avoidance System Mistakes Ships for Planes</HEAD>
