<HEAD>Move West Already Under Way for Reagan</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Reagan, who is moving to Los Angeles
after he leaves office in January, said Friday he is getting a head
start on his return to his home state.
   ``We have already started bringing a few things back from
