<TEXT>
   They're going to put former Gov. Lamar
Alexander in the movies and he says he's not sure who would be the
perfect leading man for the this-is-your-life film of his family's
trip to Australia.
   ``Robert Redford is taken in this political season,'' joked
Alexander, who wrote the book ``Six Months Off,'' purchased by
Warner Brothers Television. ``My daughter Kathryn says Chevy Chase
would be perfect.''
